Paid Medical Leave SOP
1. THE VISION
Paid Medical Leave is no longer a vacation; it is a structured, mandatory rehabilitation program. You are building a closed-loop system where we do not sign off on their continued time away from work unless they provide verifiable proof of "work" on their end: exercise, sleep, nutrition, and emotional intelligence (therapy).
2. THE DELEGATION LIST (For Bianca & Clinical Team)
